---

<BaseLayout
  title="Thermostat Repair & Replacement Lake Charles LA | Smart Thermostat Install | Latour's HVAC"
  description="Thermostat problems? Our Lake Charles technicians repair, replace, and install all types of thermostats including smart WiFi models. Call (337) 513-4425."
